	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm happy to report that I got my PowerPak today, and it works on my Famicom Titler!
<br />
<br />Of course, many games had nasty graphics glitches (I tried a few; Hebereke was pretty bad.)
<br />
<br />I put 120 Ohm resistors in my 72-&gt;60 pin adaptor, and almost all the glitches are gone.
<br />
<br />So, thanks a lot, bunnyboy!  This is a marvel of engineering!

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


