	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Based on what bunnyboy said, the resistors are preventing the bus conflict from affecting the NES (the bus conflict still occurs, but the NES doesn't see the results of it).  This is why I'm wondering if sprite DMA will work from WRAM with this mod.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


